is; saucepans; basrawi bowls and moglai katoras; laddle and zaras; mugs, vagarias, lemon juicers, and aluminum bags; pawalis, square dabbas, stock pots 83, and tubs; nonsticks; cups; tiffins; glasses; fry pans with aluminum HDL; sauce pots; basri tops; caseroles; degadas and rice stainers; charvis, kathalis, and khaldastas; aluminum housefoils; bucket kavadanis; basrai lotas and date bowls; badanas and chilamchis; butter pots; dabbas; tawas; plates/khumchas; oval and square trays; and oven dishes and basins 74. The company was incorporated in 1990 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}